                        <div class="content postcontent">
                            <input class="jpibfi" type="hidden">
<p>Nothing is better than a cupcake recipe that looks as beautiful as it tastes, but these&nbsp;<strong>strawberry shortcake cupcakes</strong>&nbsp;are just that! Moist vanilla cupcakes are filled with strawberries and then topped with a rich buttercream frosting.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Strawberry desserts are always a hit for Valentine&rsquo;s Day or parties. From simple desserts like our&nbsp;<a href="https://valentinascorner.com/strawberry-pie-recipe/">homemade strawberry pie</a>, to our&nbsp;<a href="https://valentinascorner.com/chocolate-strawberry-cake/">layered chocolate strawberry cake</a>, you can&rsquo;t go wrong with fresh strawberries!&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" src="https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5.jpg" alt="Three strawberry shortcake cupcakes, topped with a sliced strawberry. " class="wp-image-336073" title="Homemade strawberry shortcake cupcakes are the most divine dessert. These fluffy vanilla cupcakes are loaded with a sweet strawberry filling, and topped with a rich cream cheese frosting. " data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://valentinascorner.com/strawberry-shortcake-cupcakes/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Strawberry Shortcake Cupcakes" data-jpibfi-src="https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5.jpg" srcset="https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5.jpg 1200w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-450x675.jpg 450w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-100x150.jpg 100w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-270x405.jpg 270w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-150x225.jpg 150w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-226x339.jpg 226w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-54x81.jpg 54w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-108x162.jpg 108w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-360x540.jpg 360w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-540x810.jpg 540w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcake-5-720x1080.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) calc(100vw - 40px), 760px"></figure>



<p>These shortcake strawberry cupcakes are so incredible. A&nbsp;<a href="https://valentinascorner.com/vanilla-cupcake-recipe/">simple vanilla cupcake</a>&nbsp;is filled with a refreshing strawberry filling. The tarte strawberries balance the sweet cupcake beautifully, and the cherry on top is the&nbsp;<a href="https://valentinascorner.com/cream-cheese-buttercream-frosting/">cream cheese frosting</a>.&nbsp;</p>


<div class="customheading customheading-pink customheading-dark"><h2 class="ch-heading"><svg class="cicon icon-heart" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#icon-heart"></use></svg><span><strong>Why You&rsquo;ll Love This Recipe</strong></span></h2><div class="customheading-inner notop nobot">
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Seasonal.&nbsp;</strong>As strawberry season nears, there&rsquo;s no better time to make strawberry desserts.&nbsp;</li>



<li><strong>Beautiful dessert.&nbsp;</strong>The cupcakes are so appealing aesthetically to any dessert table.</li>



<li><strong>Easy peasy.&nbsp;</strong>A cupcake recipe like this is perfect for bakers of all skill levels.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

<div class="customheading customheading-pink customheading-light"><h2 class="ch-heading"><svg class="cicon icon-clipboard-list" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#icon-clipboard-list"></use></svg><span><strong>Ingredients for Strawberry Shortcake Cupcakes:</strong></span></h2><div class="customheading-inner notop nobot">
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Vanilla cupcakes &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>our&nbsp;<a href="https://valentinascorner.com/vanilla-cupcake-recipe/">classic vanilla cupcake recipe</a>&nbsp;makes the perfect cupcake.&nbsp;</li>



<li><strong>Strawberries &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>fresh strawberries are best.&nbsp;</li>



<li><strong>Vanilla frosting &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>a&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://valentinascorner.com/cream-cheese-buttercream-frosting/">homemade buttercream frosting</a></strong>&nbsp;makes the perfect frosting for these cupcakes.&nbsp;</li>



<li><strong>Strawberry glaze &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>we use store-bought strawberry jelly that we mix with diced strawberries.</li>
</ul>



<p><em>See the recipe card below for a full list of ingredients and quantities.</em></p>
</div></div>

<div class="borderbox borderbox-pink borderbox-empty ">
		<div class="borderbox-a notop nobot">	
		
<div class="customheading customheading-pink customheading-plain"><h2 class="ch-heading"><span><svg class="cicon icon-rotate" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#icon-rotate"></use></svg><span><strong>Substitutions and Variations</strong></span></span></h2><div class="customheading-inner notop nobot">
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Try out other fruits:&nbsp;</strong>Swap out strawberries with a cinnamon apple filling or even a&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://valentinascorner.com/blackberry-pie-recipe/">blackberry pie filling</a></strong>!</li>



<li><strong>Cupcake flavor:&nbsp;</strong>Switch out the vanilla cupcake for a&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://valentinascorner.com/chocolate-cupcake-recipe/">homemade chocolate cupcake</a></strong>. The flavors are just like a&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://valentinascorner.com/chocolate-covered-strawberries/">chocolate-covered strawberry</a></strong>!</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

	</div>
</div>


<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><div class="customheading customheading-pink customheading-plain"><h2 class="ch-heading"><span><strong>How to Make Strawberry Shortcake Cupcakes:&nbsp;</strong></span></h2><div class="customheading-inner notop nobot">
<p>Step-by-step instructions make this cupcake recipe as easy as can be!</p>



<div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
