. We love ours topped with this strawberry shortcake jam and sweet buttercream frosting. " data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://valentinascorner.com/strawberry-shortcake-cupcakes/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Strawberry Shortcake Cupcakes" data-jpibfi-src="https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2.jpg" srcset="https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2.jpg 1200w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2-450x675.jpg 450w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2-100x150.jpg 100w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2-270x405.jpg 270w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-2-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) calc(100vw - 40px), 760px"></noscript></figure>



<p>1 &ndash; <strong>Bake cupcakes:&nbsp;</strong>Follow our&nbsp;<a href="https://valentinascorner.com/vanilla-cupcake-recipe/">easy vanilla cupcake recipe</a>&nbsp;to make the perfect cupcakes in the oven. Allow them to cool.</p>
