tcake cupcakes that makes them so special. " data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://valentinascorner.com/strawberry-shortcake-cupcakes/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Strawberry Shortcake Cupcakes" data-jpibfi-src="https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4.jpg" srcset="https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4.jpg 1200w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4-450x675.jpg 450w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4-100x150.jpg 100w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4-270x405.jpg 270w, https://valentinascorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Strawberry-Shortcake-Cupcakes-Recipe-4-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) calc(100vw - 40px), 760px"></noscript></figure>



<p>3 &ndash; <strong>Assemble the cupcakes:&nbsp;</strong>Cut the strawberries into small pieces and combine with strawberry glaze. Hollow out the centeres of the cupcake and fill with the glaze.&nbsp;</p>
</div>



