	<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">These <strong>strawberry shortcake cupcakes</strong> are the most scrumptious dessert. Each bite of soft vanilla cupcake is full of glazed strawberries and topped with a rich cream cheese frosting. This recipe is easy to follow and will inspire you to get creative with your cupcakes.</span></div>

