			<div class="comavatar"><img alt="" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2056%2056'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-srcset="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a8bc07c0b947f062b955644a99f45c0caa95d6dd84366031ebc8c647bbc1ffc5?s=112&amp;d=blank&amp;r=g 2x" class="avatar avatar-56 photo" height="56" width="56" decoding="async" data-lazy-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a8bc07c0b947f062b955644a99f45c0caa95d6dd84366031ebc8c647bbc1ffc5?s=56&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g"><noscript><img alt="" src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a8bc07c0b947f062b955644a99f45c0caa95d6dd84366031ebc8c647bbc1ffc5?s=56&amp;d=blank&amp;r=g" srcset="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a8bc07c0b947f062b955644a99f45c0caa95d6dd84366031ebc8c647bbc1ffc5?s=112&amp;d=blank&amp;r=g 2x" class="avatar avatar-56 photo" height="56" width="56" decoding="async"></noscript></div>
			<div class="comright">
				<div class="commeta">
					<ul>
						<li class="comauth">Anna</li><!--
						--><li><time class="timeago" datetime="2024-06-22T16:02:54-04:00">June 22, 2024</time></li>					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="comcontent">
										<p>I&rsquo;m sorry but this recipe was a big fail for a beginner baker. It wasn&rsquo;t specified that the butter needed to be at room temperature for the batter. Well my butter was not at the right temperature so my batter was a grainy runny mess.  It also wasn&rsquo;t specified how much to fill the cupcake liners with batter. I filled them to the top which seemed like the logical thing to do and ended up with what looked like muffins. Please revise the recipe with more details so people who are not experienced in baking do not waste ingredients and time.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="comactions">
					<ul>
						<li class="reply smallbtn"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-88225" data-commentid="88225" data-postid="322387" data-belowelement="comment-88225" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anna" aria-label="Reply to Anna">Reply</a></li>					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</article>
<ul class="children">
